    <item>
      <title>交易员消化勒庞保证后法国市场趋于稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/french-markets-stabilize-as-traders-digest-le-pen-assurances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们权衡极右翼领导人玛丽娜·勒庞 (Marine Le Pen) 的保证，即如果她在本月晚些时候的全国大选中获胜，她将与总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 合作，法国股市收复了部分失地，债券市场趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/french-markets-stabilize-as-traders-digest-le-pen-assurances</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 09:03:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Archegos Trader 的严厉证词让 Hwang 脸上的笑容消失了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/archegos-trader-s-tough-testimony-wipes-smile-from-hwang-s-face</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在审判的大部分时间里，Archegos Capital Management 创始人 Bill Hwang 看起来并不像一个可能面临数十年监禁的人。无论是在法庭内还是法庭外，Hwang 的脸上常常挂着平静的微笑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/archegos-trader-s-tough-testimony-wipes-smile-from-hwang-s-face</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莱恩称欧洲央行认为市场正在重新定价，但不会陷入无序动态</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/ecb-sees-market-repricing-but-not-disorderly-dynamics-lane-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行首席经济学家菲利普·莱恩表示，欧洲央行认为没有理由过度担心法国最近的金融动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/ecb-sees-market-repricing-but-not-disorderly-dynamics-lane-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 08:51:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
